    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/914d9aedab4ed1584eb49a86d2911835.poster.avif?t=1771943265\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/914d9aedab4ed1584eb49a86d2911835.webm?t=1771943265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/914d9aedab4ed1584eb49a86d2911835.mp4?t=1771943265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Lootbound：冒险承担风险，组建你的队伍与构筑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一局都从独自一人开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沿着地图前进，选择你的冒险，并权衡风险与奖励。途中你会遇到同伴。与你的同伴一起，打造专属的玩法风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完美的构筑可能会无缝契合——也可能走向相反的结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/9bac39730e1d7d1bff75f7f694aa0e4a.poster.avif?t=1771943265\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/9bac39730e1d7d1bff75f7f694aa0e4a.webm?t=1771943265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/9bac39730e1d7d1bff75f7f694aa0e4a.mp4?t=1771943265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >队伍与装备</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同伴遵循与英雄相同的规则。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >物品只有在装备后才会生效。你的装备选择会直接影响队伍的行为，以及构筑整体如何运作。一件物品就可能让某个角色成为取胜关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另一件则可能把他变成累赘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/9d68fff891a0a8f9dbcc2fc02cc74a9f.poster.avif?t=1771943265\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/9d68fff891a0a8f9dbcc2fc02cc74a9f.webm?t=1771943265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/9d68fff891a0a8f9dbcc2fc02cc74a9f.mp4?t=1771943265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >物品光环</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >物品本身各自独立存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但当它们开始相互影响时才真正闪耀。有些物品带有光环，会强化相邻的物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一次好的组合足以改变整局的走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/7129577d814cc6ef2c6c9551ee99aff4.poster.avif?t=1771943265\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/7129577d814cc6ef2c6c9551ee99aff4.webm?t=1771943265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/7129577d814cc6ef2c6c9551ee99aff4.mp4?t=1771943265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >技能与成长</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的英雄从一套基础技能开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >之后获得的一切都完全由你决定。你不只是提升数值，而是在战斗中即时塑造角色的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而你的选择？不可更改。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/220044155e0f1991ed2ed24aa5d2c210.poster.avif?t=1771943265\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/220044155e0f1991ed2ed24aa5d2c210.webm?t=1771943265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091140/extras/220044155e0f1991ed2ed24aa5d2c210.mp4?t=1771943265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >伤害类型</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lootbound 中有多种伤害类型。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种类型与护甲和敌人生命值的交互方式都不同，让你可以围绕自己选择的机制来构筑：护甲穿透、疲惫、护甲破坏或直接伤害。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lootbound 是……</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款高重玩性的战术 Roguelike。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的队伍会随着游戏推进逐步组建。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带有光环与联动效果的装备。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >围绕伤害类型与物品交互打造的构筑。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过掷骰进行精确的风险与奖励选择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一局都会带来一支新队伍。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一套构筑都是你选择的直接结果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次失误都会伴随你直到最后。</p></li></ul>",
